TY  - JOUR
T1  - Managing Capacity and Inventory Jointly in Manufacturing Systems
AU  - Bradley, James R.
AU  - Glynn, Peter W.
Y1  - 2002/02/01
PY  - 2002
DA  - 2002/02/01
